OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FArchbishop of Canterbury   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fapologises over Church     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffund's link to slavery     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Archbishop of Canterbury has       
OL,6, apologised after research showed the   
OL,7, Church of England's investment fund has
OL,8, links to the slave trade.              
OL,10,FThe investigation, initiated by the    
OL,11,FChurch Commissioners, a charity        
OL,12,Fmanaging the Church's investment       
OL,13,Fportfolio, revealed that for more than 
OL,14,F100 years the fund invested large sums 
OL,15,Fof money in a company responsible for  
OL,16,Ftransporting slaves.                   
OL,18,FThe fund, known in the 18th century as 
OL,19,FQueen Anne's Bounty, has now developed 
OL,20,Finto a #10.1bn investment trust.       
